Dependencies:
  Android Tools
  Apache Ant
  CallbackAndroid

Installation:
  Configure the callbackandroid path
  Add an alias to the tools folder:
    alias pgt="~/Tools/PhoneGap-Tools/application"
    
Options:
  -p default: null
  Project path

  -t default: null
  Target 

  -c default: Off
  Create application

  -b default: Off
  Build application

  -d default: Off
  Deploy application

  -r default: Off
  Run application
  
Usage:
  Create application
  pgt -c
  
  Build, install application
  pgt -bdr 

  Run application on myemulator
  pgt -r -t "myemulator" -p "my/project/path/"